'''保羅·L·D·布萊爾'''（{{lang-en|Paul L. D. Blair}}，{{bd|1944年|2月1日|2013年|12月26日|catIdx=Blair}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手。生涯前期皆效力於金鶯隊，成為1960年代金鶯王朝的中外野手。生涯後期曾轉戰效力過紅人與洋基等隊，並幫助洋基拿下2連霸。<ref name="Post">News services and staff reports (December 28, 2013) [https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/paul-blair-graceful-orioles-outfielder-dies-at-69/2013/12/27/3864482c-6f13-11e3-aecc-85cb037b7236_story.html?tid=auto_complete "Star center fielder won two titles with Orioles"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/paul-blair-graceful-orioles-outfielder-dies-at-69/2013/12/27/3864482c-6f13-11e3-aecc-85cb037b7236_story.html?tid=auto_complete |date=20160311040226 }} ''The Washington Post'', page B4. Retrieved December 28, 2013</ref>

布萊爾曾8度拿下金手套獎，其中1969年至1975年間更是拿下金手套7連霸。<ref name="mklingamantbs">Klingaman, Mike. [http://weblogs.baltimoresun.com/sports/thetoydepartment/2010/05/catching_up_with_former_oriole_8.html "Catching Up With...Former Oriole Paul Blair"] {{Wayback|url=http://weblogs.baltimoresun.com/sports/thetoydepartment/2010/05/catching_up_with_former_oriole_8.html |date=20160430175502 }}, ''The Toy Department'' (''The Baltimore Sun'' sports blog), Tuesday, May 4, 2010</ref>他也被認為是一名飛球追蹤能力很出色的選手。<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/28/sports/baseball/paul-blair-center-fielder-for-champions-dies-at-69.html?hpw&rref=obituaries obituary] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/28/sports/baseball/paul-blair-center-fielder-for-champions-dies-at-69.html?hpw&rref=obituaries |date=20131229231930 }} ''NY Times'' Retrieved 2013-12-27</ref>1984年，他入選金鶯隊名人堂。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/orioles/history/orioles-hall-of-fame |title=Baltimore Orioles Hall of Fame at MLB.com |publisher=mlb.com |accessdate=10 December 2019 |archive-date=2018-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130013828/https://www.mlb.com/orioles/history/orioles-hall-of-fame |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==職業生涯==
1965年，布萊爾進入球隊先發輪值。該年他的打擊率為2成34，並敲出5轟與25分打點。1966年，他的打擊率為2成77。這年金鶯隊在[[法蘭克·羅賓森|法蘭克·羅賓森]]的帶領下於世界大賽四連勝橫掃道奇奪冠。布萊爾在第三場敲出致勝全壘打，並在第四場沒收[[吉姆·拉斐爾|吉姆·拉斐爾]]的追平全壘打。

1967年，布萊爾的打擊率為生涯新高的2成93，並敲出11轟與64分打點。另外他也擊出聯盟最多的12支三壘安打，並收穫生涯首座金手套獎。1968年，布萊爾陷入低潮，打擊率僅2成11。不過他在1969年打出精彩的一季，打擊率為2成85，並敲出生涯新高的26轟與76分打點。這年他也成為金鶯隊史首位達成單季20轟20盜的球員。<ref>[https://www.mlb.com/news/jonathan-villar-joins-20-20-club-orioles-beat-rays Trezza, Joe. "Villar joins 20-20 club as O's rout Rays," MLB.com, Sunday, August 25, 2019.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/jonathan-villar-joins-20-20-club-orioles-beat-rays |date=20201209100741 }} Retrieved August 25, 2019</ref>而他也入選生涯首次明星賽。金鶯隊在這年拿下美東冠軍，[[1969年美國聯盟冠軍賽|1969年美國聯盟冠軍賽]]第三場，布萊爾敲出5支安打，幫助金鶯橫掃雙城。<ref>{{cite web|title=Congratulations to Two Postseason Record Setters: Carl Crawford of the Tampa Bay Rays and Matt Stairs of the Philadelphia Phillies|url=http://www.baseballlibrary.com/columns/column.php?id=236|work=BaseballLibrary.com|accessdate=13 December 2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121118181935/http://www.baseballlibrary.com/columns/column.php?id=236|archivedate=2012-11-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過他在世界大賽僅敲出2支安打，打擊率僅1成。最後金鶯1勝4敗輸給大都會。

1970年5月31日，布萊爾被觸身球擊中臉部，造成他鼻子、顴骨斷裂以及眼眶受傷，他也休息了3個禮拜才康復。<ref name="blairtatumupi">[https://www.nytimes.com/1970/06/01/archives/angels-triumph-over-orioles-61-blair-is-injured.html "Angels Triumph Over Orioles, 6‐1; Blair Is Injured," ''United Press International'' (UPI), Sunday, May 31, 1970.] Retrieved October 15, 2020</ref><ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1873&dat=19700604&id=1YYeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=oMsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=766,718616 "Tatum Apologizes For Blair Beaning," ''The Associated Press'' (AP), Thursday, June 4, 1970.] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1873&dat=19700604&id=1YYeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=oMsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=766,718616 |date=20201019100353 }} Retrieved October 15, 2020</ref><ref>[https://www.masnsports.com/orioles-buzz/2013/12/in-os-glory-years-blair-made-the-impossible-grabs-seem-routine.html Kerzel, Pete. "In O’s glory years, Blair made the impossible grabs seem routine," Mid-Atlantic Sports Network (MASN), Thursday, December 26, 2013.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.masnsports.com/orioles-buzz/2013/12/in-os-glory-years-blair-made-the-impossible-grabs-seem-routine.html |date=20201018171237 }} Retrieved October 15, 2020</ref>該年他的打擊率為2成67，這年金鶯隊再次闖進季後賽。雖然布萊爾在美聯冠軍賽僅敲出1支安打，<ref>[https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1970_ALCS.shtml 1970 American League Championship Series: Baltimore Orioles over Minnesota Twins (3–0) – Baseball-Reference.com.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1970_ALCS.shtml |date=20080623064200 }} Retrieved October 15, 2020</ref>不過他在世界大賽的打擊率高達4成74，上壘率5成24。金鶯隊也以4勝1敗拿下世界大賽冠軍。<ref>[https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1970_WS.shtml 1970 World Series: Baltimore Orioles over Cincinnati Reds (4–1) – Baseball-Reference.com.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1970_WS.shtml |date=20110808163845 }} Retrieved October 15, 2020</ref>

[[File:Blair,_Paul_(2007).jpg|thumb]]
1971年，布萊爾嘗試改成左右開弓，結果他的打擊率跌破2成，迫使他放棄這個打擊方式。該年他的打擊率為2成62，金鶯隊又一次打進世界大賽，不過最後鏖戰7場比賽不敵海盜。這年布萊爾也寫下一項紀錄，他成為史上第一位在世界大賽夜間比賽上場的球員。

1969年至1975年間，布萊爾都拿下了金手套獎。寫下了金鶯隊史連續拿下金手套獎的次高紀錄。

1977年1月20日，洋基隊用Elliott Maddox和Rick Bladt向金鶯隊交易布萊爾。<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/1977/01/21/archives/yanks-get-blair-for-maddox-yankees-trade-maddox-settle-munson.html Chass, Murray. "Yanks Get Blair for Maddox," ''The New York Times'', Friday, January 21, 1977.] Retrieved October 16, 2020</ref>這年洋基隊戰力再度升級，連續兩年闖進世界大賽。而布萊爾在第一場比賽於延長賽敲出再見安打贏球，<ref>[https://www.mlb.com/video/yanks-win-game-1-on-blairs-hit/c-25630959 ABC's telecast of Paul Blair's walkoff RBI single to left off Rick Rhoden in the New York Yankees' Game 1 victory over Los Angeles Dodgers at Yankee Stadium in the 1977 World Series – MLB.com.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.mlb.com/video/yanks-win-game-1-on-blairs-hit/c-25630959 |date=20190826021323 }} Retrieved August 25, 2019</ref>洋基最終也順利拿下睽違已久的世界大賽冠軍。

1978年，在洋基隊拿下冠軍2連霸後，布萊爾在1979年初被球隊釋出。不過紅人隊隨即網羅了他，打了一個球季後，布萊爾再度回到洋基隊。1980年，布萊爾第二度被洋基隊釋出後，他正式宣布退休。

布萊爾生涯打擊率為2成50，並敲出134轟與1513支安打。另有171次盜壘成功。而他也是一名出色的短打者，他曾在1975年敲出17支觸擊安打。
==晚年與逝世==
退休後，布萊爾與妻子住在馬里蘭州的伍斯托克。<ref name="Post"/>日後他也常出席一些名人高球賽或保齡球賽的場合。<ref name="Post"/>他的兒子保羅·布萊爾三世曾在巨人隊和小熊隊小聯盟打了8個球季。

2013年12月26日，布萊爾在進行保齡球比賽途中因心臟病發倒下。他也隨即送往醫院急救，不過最終不治身亡，享年69歲。<ref name="Post"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxsports.com/mlb/story/four-time-world-series-champion-blair-dies-at-age-69-122613|title=Four-time World Series champion Blair dies at age 69|work=[[FOX_Sports|FOX Sports]]|date=26 December 2013|accessdate=2020-11-29|archive-date=2016-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410190538/http://www.foxsports.com/mlb/story/four-time-world-series-champion-blair-dies-at-age-69-122613|dead-url=no}}</ref>
